ZH: 暖气是我家里冬天必备的设备。
EN: Heating is a necessary equipment in my house during winter.

ZH: 我们可以把暖气调高一点吗？
EN: Can we turn up the heating a little bit?

ZH: 暖气坏了，我们需要请修理工来修理。
EN: The heating is broken, we need to call a repairman to fix it.

ZH: 我们家的暖气节能环保。
EN: The heating in our house is energy-efficient and environmentally friendly.

ZH: 我在床边放了一个暖气片，晚上脚不会冷。
EN: I placed a radiator by my bed, so my feet won't be cold at night.

ZH: 请确保暖气在离开家之前关闭。
EN: Please make sure to turn off the heating before leaving the house.

ZH: 下午的时候气温会升高，不需要开暖气。
EN: The temperature will rise in the afternoon, so we don't need to turn on the heating.

ZH: 暖气片里正在流动的热水能帮助空气升温。
EN: The hot water circulating in the radiator helps to warm up the air.

ZH: 我觉得房间里的暖气不够暖。
EN: I feel like the heating in the room is not warm enough.

ZH: 空调也能起到暖气的作用。
EN: The air conditioner can also act as a heater.

ZH: 我们的办公室有中央暖气系统。
EN: Our office has a central heating system.

ZH: 早上起床的时候暖气还没有开启。
EN: The heating is not on when I wake up in the morning.

ZH: 暖气温度可以用一个调温器来控制。
EN: The temperature of the heating can be controlled using a thermostat.

ZH: 暖气片需要定期清洁以保持有效运转。
EN: The radiator needs to be cleaned regularly to maintain proper functioning.

ZH: 暖气的散热效果很好。
EN: The heating has a good heat dissipation effect.

ZH: 我们家的暖气是通过燃气来提供热量的。
EN: The heating in our house is provided by gas.

ZH: 突然停电了，暖气也不起作用了。
EN: The power suddenly went off, and the heating stopped working as well.

ZH: 暖气呼呼地响着, 把整个房间都温暖起来了。
EN: The heating is humming and warming up the entire room.

ZH: 暖气热乎乎的，感觉很舒适。
EN: The room is warm and cozy with the heating on.
